    public class DistNetworkImpl
extends NetworkImpl<DistBus,DistBranch>
implements DistNetwork
    An implementation of the model object 'Dist Network'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Positive Seq Data Only
    • Sc Std
    • Load Schedule Data
    • Sc Point Net Data
    • Fault Net
